{
  "stem": "4189.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when we got back, all those people that were there that we saw, those skeletons, they were all dead.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had injected them with, with air in the veins and killed them all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our job was to bury them in those ditches that we dug.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's why they took us over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they wrapped each body up in a blanket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And four prisoners had to carry one, one body out into the woods there in the clearing and bury them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then by the time we got back to the camp, it was morning already.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was all done during the night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then in the morning when we got back, it was dawn already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The camp was empty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no prisoners there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the guards had loaded all their belongings on wagons.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "See, they were going to evacuate this camp but they had no trucks and no cars, because all the trucks and cars were all confiscated for the army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they had wagons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they wanted us to push those wagons with their belongings further west.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's what we had to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They evacuated us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to go and push those wagons all day long to further west, constantly going west.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they did not want to fall into Russian hands.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, they, if they were going to be captured, they'd rather be captured by the Americans or the English, not by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't like the Russians.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So finally, we ended up in a town of Hirschberg, which is also in Germany, near the Czechoslovakian border.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was also another camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From that camp, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we went to a town called Reichenau.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
